   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"That we (?) may know that I have appointed Serenos to complete the tax (?). I do not appoint him over you that he may (?) give something in your behalf. But give the allottment, your payment. Collect it. Take it. For if you seek to default it (?) respecting anything on it, I shall send one who will bring it out of your bones."</ab>
         </div>
